    <item>
      <title>[筆記] ansible 設定 ssh_args 開啟 ForwardX11 / config ansible ssh_args to enable forwardagent</title>
      <link>https://blog.cowbay.org/p/%E7%AD%86%E8%A8%98-ansible-%E8%A8%AD%E5%AE%9A-ssh_args-%E9%96%8B%E5%95%9F-forwardx11-/-config-ansible-ssh_args-to-enable-forwardagent/</link>
